I would classify these as fighters as they are generally more fragile (without items) than the champs I've listed above for the bruisers as they normally rely on a ability in their kit to avoid damage and counter. Much of their damage mitigation comes from pursuing and committing to their target, forcing them to to stay in combat with their opponent.

The line between Fighter/Juggernaut/Bruiser/etc. is very hazy as a handful of champs can straddle these lines easily.
